# Filament Resource Table Conventions

When creating or modifying a Filament resource with a table, always disable row click navigation:

```php
return $table
    ->columns([...])
    ->filters([...])
    ->actions([...])
    ->bulkActions([...])
    ->recordUrl(null);
```

`->recordUrl(null)` must be chained at the end of every table definition. Clicking a table row should never trigger navigation.
